{"id": 1136, "genre": 1001, "title": "你对便利店最大的不满是什么？", "description": "怎么还没开到我的城市来！（题图来自：Sergiy Maidukov）", "record_count": 3780, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160729160335UNr5ciPnk9R3mT4I.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-30T17:00:20Z", "options": [{"id": 103168, "content": "煙比較貴", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697080}, {"id": 103424, "content": "态度特别差！特别差", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698138}, {"id": 103170, "content": "冷门时段便当不全", "image": null, "praise_count": 141, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333488}, {"id": 103426, "content": "我的城市没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697786}, {"id": 103682, "content": "便利店很好呀，方便，而且有些东西商场没有，像711或屈臣氏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699057}, {"id": 103172, "content": "满不满意大多数取决于收银员的服务态度", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668897}, {"id": 103173, "content": "不喜欢用Apple Pay的，喜欢扫码?", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603240}, {"id": 103174, "content": "集点的东西不如国外", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678068}, {"id": 104454, "content": "缺少某些商品的独家独家性，与传统大型商超比，便利店更应该具有便利性和商品独特性", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700129}, {"id": 103175, "content": "便利店到底卖什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697458}, {"id": 103431, "content": "全都卖关东煮，就不能卖点肉夹馍。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671303}, {"id": 103177, "content": "大陆不提供打印复印！", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262280}, {"id": 103433, "content": "便利店是个伟大的工作，但是很多店员只是把它看作高级士多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686065}, {"id": 103178, "content": "很便利，也很麻烦（后期影响）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667933}, {"id": 103435, "content": "东西略贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677641}, {"id": 102668, "content": "收银员慢腾腾爱理不理", "image": null, "praise_count": 174, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 103436, "content": "没有日本的便利店好吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685868}, {"id": 102669, "content": "三件八折的面包并不好吃，也不新鲜", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 103181, "content": "不像日本有很多便利店自营自制美食。", "image": null, "praise_count": 153, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476254}, {"id": 102670, "content": "盒饭不好吃，热完汤还是半凝固状态", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 103438, "content": "少", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698171}, {"id": 102671, "content": "包子面粉不好，通常不买", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 103439, "content": "贵，但是却不怎么好吃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 356515}, {"id": 103695, "content": "快餐难吃死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699243}, {"id": 103696, "content": "东西不全. 需要的没有. 没用的一大堆.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699141}, {"id": 102673, "content": "推出的合作款太丑，毫无积点兑换的动力", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 103185, "content": "东西太少，价格小贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419840}, {"id": 103441, "content": "都装饰得特好看「简购连锁便利店」，但是对商品进购却不怎么用心，就是在便利店里找不到想要的东西，还是更喜欢「沃尔玛购物超市」", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698152}, {"id": 103186, "content": "鱼蛋，豆腐串像煮了一千年的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 186, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465792}, {"id": 103442, "content": "没有标价签。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693717}, {"id": 105490, "content": "态度差还长的丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607959}, {"id": 103187, "content": "可能连歪果仁自己也不愿意去卖", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118643}, {"id": 103443, "content": "体谅为主吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696381}, {"id": 107795, "content": "太小了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715687}, {"id": 103188, "content": "没卖避孕套有时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 629867}, {"id": 103189, "content": "水果不多", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623377}, {"id": 105749, "content": "东西普遍较贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707514}, {"id": 103191, "content": "独缺你当时最需要的那个", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688316}, {"id": 103192, "content": "每个工作日的早上都要排很长的队", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672522}, {"id": 103448, "content": "只卖套子，不卖...", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226501}, {"id": 103193, "content": "阿婆用手直接串热狗>_<", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687549}, {"id": 103450, "content": "面包蛋糕都是同一种口味，长相不一样摆了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698197}, {"id": 103451, "content": "人多在狭小的通道里拥挤 错过了根本没法回头拿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436982}, {"id": 106779, "content": "老板抠门，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711860}, {"id": 103196, "content": "陈旧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697482}, {"id": 103452, "content": "加热炉完东西太烫手，有没有什么关怀措施。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect"